
msgid ""
"Controls how this node determines its role in the mesh.\n"
"Force routed portal (MRP): always acts as IPv4 NAT gateway regardless of upstream.\n"
"Auto detect (default): portal if upstream WAN is active, otherwise layer-2 bridge peer.\n"
"CPE mode: treats mesh backhaul as upstream WAN; creates its own NAT subnet Forces VXLAN tunnel off.\n"
"Bridge VXLAN trunk portal (MBP): bridged (no-NAT) portal; adds WAN port to vxtunnel bridge.\n"
"Bridge VXLAN trunk peer (TPN): peer node; adds WAN port to vxtunnel bridge."
msgstr ""
"控制本节点在 Mesh 网络中的角色模式。\n"
"强制路由门户（MRP）：无论上游是否连通，始终作为 IPv4 NAT 网关。\n"
"自动检测（默认）：上游 WAN 有网络时作为门户（Portal），否则作为二层桥接 Peer 节点。\n"
"CPE 模式：将 Mesh 回程视为上游 WAN，创建独立的 NAT 子网，并强制关闭 VXLAN 隧道。\n"
"桥接 VXLAN 主干门户（MBP）：无 NAT 的桥接门户，将 WAN 端口加入 vxtunnel 桥接。\n"
"桥接 VXLAN 主干 Peer（TPN）：Peer 节点，将 WAN 端口加入 vxtunnel 桥接。"
